[Student "S"]
{WEST opens 2\C.

EAST should just respond 2NT, even with 11 points. The idea is to make a positive response (which forces 
the partnership to game level), and show extra strength later.

This time there is no need. WEST should bid 4\C (Gerber), and EAST answers 4\S for 
two Aces.

Next WEST should ask for Kings, and when EAST shows one King WEST should bid 7NT.}

